<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Problem Card 1: 84 kg. Sample response: I used an algorithm to subtract 36 from 120.</p>
<p>Problem Card 2: 49 kg. Sample response: I drew a diagram and realized I needed to subtract 67 from 116.</p>
  </solution>


